'''Gray Squadron''' was an experimental unit of six [[Aleph-class starfighter|''Aleph''-class starfighters]] based on ''[[Blue Diver]]'' in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]]. [[Syal Antilles]], [[Zueb Zan]] and [[Unidentified R2 unit (Gray Squadron)|their astromech]] were in the squadron. They fought at the [[Battle of Tralus (Second Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Tralus]].

